===Analysis===
'''Pola Kai'''

Priority: '''High'''

:At first remodel, this Italian heavy cruiser has good Firepower but a very low Torpedo stat, making her suited for daytime surface combat thanks to [[Artillery Spotting]] but not so much for night battle.
:What makes her incredibly valuable is the unique ability to carry seaplane fighters and bombers without being classified as an aviation cruiser, making her able to contest air control where other ships just aren't allowed to go.
:Keep in mind that she has inherently long range when shelling order is an issue.

:No further remodels have been implemented for her yet (as of November 2020).


====Recommended Roles====
* Air superiority
* Surface combat

====Not Recommended Roles====
* Night battle

===Important Info===
* She comes with the [[Ro.44 Seaplane Fighter]] at Kai.

